README for hexchat


NOTES

  Optional software for special features:

  dbus-glib:       Used for single-instance and scripting interface
  enchant:         Spell check
  iso-codes:       Display language names instead of codes
  lua:             Lua scripting plugin
  libcanberra:     Support for sound alerts
  libnotify:       Support for freedesktop notifications
  libproxy:        Support for getting proxy information
  pciutils:        System information plugin


End of file.
